Sentencas: A portable solid oxide fuel cell using butane gas as fuel was demonstrated.
Titulo: Portable solid oxide fuel cells using butane gas as fuel

Sentencas: A yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) tube (7 mm in diameter and 90 mm in length) was used as the electrolyte with a porous Pt cathode and a Ni-YSZ cermet anode.
Titulo: Portable solid oxide fuel cells using butane gas as fuel

Sentencas: The cell showed an output power of 0.14 W using a commercial butane gas bomb.
Titulo: Portable solid oxide fuel cells using butane gas as fuel
